  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK969">
<l>mayirnīppiṉ vāḻāk kavarimā vaṉṉā</l>
<l>ruyirnīppar māṉam variṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who give up (their) life when (their) honour is at stake are like the yark which kills itself at the loss of (even one of) its hairs.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
